#Soalan 3 (Lebih daripada satu operasi)
#Create a Python program that receives two numbers from the user and displays:
#the sum
#the difference
#the product

Jawapan :
num1 = float(input("Enter first number: "))
num2 = float(input("Enter second number: "))

sum =  num1 + num2 
difference = num1 - num2
product = num1 * num2

print("The sum is:", + sum)
print ("The difference is:", + difference)
print("The product is:", + product)
